title: Copilot Live Premium Europe 9.6.2.807 Patched
description:
Here are the instructions which are also included in the torrent:
1. Install CoPilot_9.4.0.144 to your phone.
2. Make an account
3. Uninstall CoPilot_9.4.0.144 from your phone.
4.Turn Wifi and Data off.
5. Install CoPilot.GPS.v.9.6.2.807_LVL.
6. Turn Wifi or Data on, for login purposes.
7. Log in with the same existing account you created in step 2.
8. Download maps... WIFI strongly recommended.
9. Enjoy
